--[[
    Ice Hub Library
    A Roblox UI library — pixel-perfect recreation of Ice Hub aesthetic.
    
    Features:
      - Full Rayfield-compatible API (CreateWindow, CreateTab, all elements)
      - Quick Access mini-GUI with star-pinning
      - Per-row: reset (X), star (☆→★), keybind pill, toggle/action
      - Theme switcher (Dark / Midnight / Frost / Ember)
      - Notification system
      - Key system
      - Config saving / loading
      - Minimize, close, drag
      - Toggle-key to show/hide
]]

